#
# User-Agent in spider of python
#
1) diffrent User-Agent sees different content.

2) User-Agent is different in python for mobile browser, PC browser,
        for different browsers such as Safari, Firefox, Chrome, IE etc.
        
        Safari 5.1 on MAC:
            User-Agent:Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10_6_8; en-us) 
            AppleWebKit/534.50 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/5.1 Safari/534.50
            
        Firefox 4.0.1 on MAC:
            User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10.6; rv:2.0.1) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/4.0.1
            
        Chrome 17.0 on MAC:
            User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_7_0) 
            AppleWebKit/535.11 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/17.0.963.56 Safari/535.11
            
        IE 11 on Windows:
            User-Agent:Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; WOW64; Trident/7.0; .NET4.0C;
            .NET4.0E; .NET CLR 2.0.50727; .NET CLR 3.0.30729; .NET CLR 3.5.30729; InfoPath.3; rv:11.0) like Gecko
            
        mobile: ...
        
# ref:  Python爬虫：常用浏览器的useragent    https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/21252983?refer=gooseeker

